{"hash":"78233c70288de5cc80ede0d03ef7918cb4b6eee5","data":{"tag":{"title":"Terminal","belongsTo":{"edges":[{"node":{"title":"[TIP] Visual Studio Code 터미널 실행","path":"/01-tip-visualcode/","date":"13. December 2020","timeToRead":1,"description":"터미널에서 비주얼 코드 실행 방법입니다.","content":"<h1 id=\"visual-studio-code-터미널-실행\"><a href=\"#visual-studio-code-%ED%84%B0%EB%AF%B8%EB%84%90-%EC%8B%A4%ED%96%89\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Visual Studio Code 터미널 실행</h1>\n<p>항상 초기 터미널 세팅을 할 때, 반드시 하는 세팅 중 하나인데 자주 까먹어서 작성합니다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"진행-순서\"><a href=\"#%EC%A7%84%ED%96%89-%EC%88%9C%EC%84%9C\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>진행 순서</h2>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Visual Studio Code</strong> 실행</li>\n<li><strong>Command Pallete</strong>를 엽니다.</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>Mac : <code class=\"language-text\">shift</code> + <code class=\"language-text\">command</code> + <code class=\"language-text\">P</code></li>\n</ul>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li><strong>Shell Command</strong> 를 입력해서 <code class=\"language-text\">[Shell Command: Install &#39;code&#39; command in PATH]</code> 를 실행합니다.</li>\n<li>터미널에서 원하는 디렉토리에서 <code class=\"language-text\">[code .]</code>를 입력시 실행가능합니다.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/42582516/102009071-5b2d5700-3d78-11eb-930e-bbf835c4f60c.png\" alt=\"shell command\"></p>\n<hr>\n<p>좋은 단축키 목록</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://zellwk.com/blog/useful-vscode-keyboard-shortcuts/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://zellwk.com/blog/useful-vscode-keyboard-shortcuts/</a></li>\n</ul>\n"}}]}}},"context":{}}